WEBVTT

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:30.576
Not the lowercase,
muttered-behind-my-back kind,

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.976
or the seemingly harmless
chubby or cuddly.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:38.600
I'm not even the more sophisticated
voluptuous or curvaceous kind.

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:41.696
Let's not sugarcoat it.

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:45.576
I am the capital F-A-T kind of fat.

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:48.200
I am the elephant in the room.

00:00:50.040 --> 00:00:51.576
When I walked out on stage,

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.296
some of you may have been thinking,

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:55.736
"Aww, this is going to be hilarious,

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:58.376
because everybody knows
that fat people are funny."

00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:00.416
(Laughter)